      <item>
        <title>Using a CDN for list.module and site.module JS files</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[juanma]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/parth.nextbits">@parth.nextbits</a>,</p>
<p>It seems that the G-Metrix tool is not reporting this correctly.</p>
<p>If you go to <a href="http://frontity.org">frontity.org</a> and open the network tab in your browser console you should see that the same asset is served with the <code>x-vercel-cache: HIT</code> which means that <a href="https://vercel.com/docs/edge-network/caching#x-vercel-cache">this response was served “from the edge”</a> (from the CDN).</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff" title="Screen Shot 2020-11-04 at 6.57.24 PM"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff_2_517x324.png" alt="Screen Shot 2020-11-04 at 6.57.24 PM" data-base62-sha1="2JXPlNv2NKBt25y6nic61WFoEaz" width="517" height="324" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff_2_517x324.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff_2_775x486.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff_2_1034x648.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/13367ee0823969e944d64377747491df7eaddeff_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Maybe you have to specify the CDN in the “User Settings”<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf" title="Screen Shot 2020-11-04 at 7.01.17 PM"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf_2_690x198.png" alt="Screen Shot 2020-11-04 at 7.01.17 PM" data-base62-sha1="8E3wwMCzQJ9cBT9BN1m7q8vWwh1" width="690" height="198" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf_2_690x198.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf_2_1035x297.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf_2_1380x396.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3c989186fc11e30ecc46a906130e17f342ff0cbf_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
